281343,"uid":266388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"通識教育科係董生你當年仲係特首的時間推出的. <br />\n諮詢時間 2004年10月 至 2005年1月19日<br />\n下台時間 2005年3月<br />\n<br />\n2004年10月 高中及高等教育新學制 － 第一階段諮詢文件 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cs-curriculum-doc-report/about-cs-curriculum-doc-report/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fcs-curriculum-doc-report%2Fabout-cs-curriculum-doc-report%2Findex.html&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=34f46165\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/cs-curriculum-doc-report/about-cs-curriculum-doc-report/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政府當局於2004年10月發表題為&quot;改革高中及高等教育學<br />\n制 &quot;的諮詢文件。該諮詢文件載述 334學制的設計藍圖、推行時間<br />\n表及財務安排。諮詢期於2005年1月19日結束。<br />\n新高中課程下設有4個核心科目，分別是中國語文科、英<br />\n國語文科、數學科及通識教育科。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr08-09/chinese/panels/ed/papers/ed0711cb2-2122-2-c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr08-09%2Fchinese%2Fpanels%2Fed%2Fpapers%2Fed0711cb2-2122-2-c.pdf&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=317732fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr08-09/chinese/panels/ed/papers/ed0711cb2-2122-2-c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"fcc7b6738fc2bd1e2e30bc5a50f095dacf984528","tid":1281343,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:31:07.000Z","msg":"通識好似係佢任內研究嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac76327f75526c4f1980aca65eaa0cc83c21dc7","tid":1281343,"uid":257466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:32:10.000Z","msg":"老實，通識只係客觀地將事實講出黎，例如功能組別、法治定義、小圈子選舉。如果學生知道之後會「以為自己大晒」，咁就係香港政府嘅失敗"},{"pid":"bb6b17edd0eec33e9c2af1801988f4e0d11a7af1","tid":1281343,"uid":44277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:32:17.000Z","msg":"講到教完啲學生就識咁<br />\n係就唔會咁多人中英文唔合格啦"},{"pid":"395af05de72d52fb81da6c12a45807967a367563","tid":1281343,"uid":25089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T09:34:46.000Z","msg":"原來幕後主謀係董生<br />\n我終於明子華點解明佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}